columnConfigurations.columnName: PO item w/o agreement or info record (%)
columnConfigurations.columnAlias: PO item w/o agreement or info record (%)

dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until GR created (days)",
    "Time until supplier invoice created (days)",
    "PO item w/o material number (%)",
    "PO item w/o agreement or info record (%)",
    "Late GR creation (%)",
    "Early GR creation (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Goods receipts created") 
        	AS "Time until GR created (days)",
		AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Supplier invoices created") 
        	AS "Time until supplier invoice created (days)",
		AVG ("3 - Info - Purchase order items without material number") * 100 
        	AS "PO item w/o material number (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Purchase order items without agreement or purchasing info record") * 100 
        	AS "PO item w/o agreement or info record (%)",
		AVG ("3 - Info - Purchase order items without outline agreement") * 100 
        	AS "PO item w/o outline agreement (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Purchase order items rejected") * 100 
        	AS "PO rejection rate (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Goods receipt created later than planned") * 100 
        	AS "Late GR creation (%)",
		AVG ("2 - Blocker - Goods receipt created earlier than planned") * 100 
        	AS "Early GR creation (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
